snippet.title: Axon TD: Uprising Launch Trailer - September 27th!
snippet.description:
Axon TD: Uprising comes out of Early Access and into Official Release on Friday, September 27th! It features:
- 40 Unique Defenses
- A story driven Campaign comprised of 40 Missions
- Roguelite Survival Mode
- Dozens of maps
- Up to 4 Player Co-op
- Leaderboards
- And a Map Editor with Steam Workshop support!

Buy Axon TD: Uprising on the Steam Store: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2296550/Axon_TD_Uprising__Tower_Defense/

Join our Discord here:
https://discord.gg/W7FWK8w
